CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 9, 1958, pg. A15, reads: "Another Group of Frog Guests included (front center and clockwise) Mr. and Mrs. Cooper Johnson, the Robert Youngs, the Clarence L. Halls, Ben Frazier, the Luke McDaniels and Mrs. Frazier. - Teenie Harris Photo."The Frogs (Friendly Rivalry Often Generates Success) is a mens' social club organized in 1910.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, clockwise from front center: Mr. and Mrs. Cooper Johnson, Mr. and Mrs. Robert Young, Mr. and Mrs. Clarence L. Hall, Ben Frazier, Mr. and Mrs. Luke McDaniels, and Mrs. Frazier, seated around banquet table for FROGS event, Gateway Plaza
